      This method is used to check whether two methods are the same.

    • checkParameters

      This method is used to check whether two methods have the same parameters.
      参数:
      parameters1 - the list of parameters of the first method
      parameters2 - the list of parameters of the second method
      返回:
      true if the two methods have the same parameters, false otherwise
